Pakistani authorities discovered on Saturday a supposedly leading head of a conspiracy aimed at sending five men from northern Virginia to Afghanistan to kill US soldiers, saying that they hope this case could help uncover an extensive network of terrorist recruiters searching the Internet for radicalized young men.
