Affaire Liliane Bettencourt : François-Marie Banier condemned for exploitation of weakness
On Friday, the Nanterre Court decided to judge the artist François-Marie Banier in order to determine whether, as the daughter of the billionaire Liliane Bettencourt claims, he took advantage of a weak moment of the eighty-year-olds to sneak up on some of her assets.
